 (desogestrel-ethinyl estradiol)." Ortho McNeil Pharmaceutical  (2001):|"Product Information. Demulen 1/50 (ethinyl estradiol-ethynodiol)." Searle|"Product Information. Triphasil (ethinyl estradiol-levonorgestrel)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories  (2001):|"Product Information. Ortho-Cyclen (ethinyl estradiol-norgestimate)." Ortho McNeil Pharmaceutical  (2001):|"Product Information. Lo/Ovral (ethinyl estradiol-norgestrel)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories  (2001):|"Product Information. Norplant System (levonorgestrel)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories  (2001):|"Product Information. Micronor (norethindrone)." Ortho McNeil Pharmaceutical  (2001):|"Product Information. Ovrette (norgestrel)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories  (2001):', 'DDInter', 0);
